/span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5446196\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5446196\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vfp1701664033439.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vfp1701664033439.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vfp1701664033439.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vfp1701664033439\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This section, of which multiple are defined in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uproperties.ini</code>\n\t\tfile, defines a single property definition used by the Property Inspector of the DSP\n\t\tComponent Editor in the IDE.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vfp1701664033439__section_y2r_5nr_qzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d509580e52\">Syntax</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vfp1701664033439_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vfp1701664033439__codeblock_osr_vnr_qzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[PropertyId]=<em class=\"ph i\">[html:title]</em>\ndescription=<em class=\"ph i\">Description</em>\ncategory=<em class=\"ph i\">Category</em>\ntooltip=<em class=\"ph i\">Tooltip</em>\ndatatype=<em class=\"ph i\">DataType</em>\nchoice=<em class=\"ph i\">Choice</em>\nentries=<em class=\"ph i\">Entries</em>\naltchoice=<em class=\"ph i\">AlternativeChoice</em></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"p\">See the following table for syntax description:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vfp1701664033439__table_bmv_znr_qzb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Syntax</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><em class=\"ph i\">PropertyId</em></td>\n<td class=\"entry\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specifies the physical property id as it is maintained in the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tproperty list and supplied to your widget.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The <code class=\"ph codeph\">PropertyId</code> is often prefixed with either\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">html</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">style</span>,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tor <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">class</span> separated by a colon. Other\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tprefixes are also allowed but do not have a special treatment in\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tUniface. For example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">html:title</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The <code class=\"ph codeph\">grp</code> keyword is not allowed, as this is reserved for property\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tgroups. </p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The following keywords are not allowed as\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">PropertyId</code>:<code class=\"ph codeph\">propertydatatypes</code>,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">propertygroups</code>. The\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">PropertyId</code> is always send in lower case to\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe browser, regardless of how it is defined. It is good\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpractice to not use camelcase for <code class=\"ph codeph\">PropertyIds</code>,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbut instead use hyphens (-) or underscores (_) as word\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tseparators.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><em class=\"ph i\">Description </em></td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Specifies a more descriptive name or description of the property.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIt should be short, a single line, and is allowed to contain\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tspaces.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><em class=\"ph i\">Category</em></td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Specifies in which tab (category) the property will appear in the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tProperty Inspector.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><em class=\"ph i\">Tooltip</em></td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Specifies a more extensive description of the property. It might\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tinclude a syntax or a reference to a standard W3C website describing\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe property. Sometimes it is useful to provide some examples. Use a\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsemicolon to break your tooltip into multiple lines.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><em class=\"ph i\">Datatype</em></td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Specifies the editing experience provided by the Property Inspector. Possible data\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\ttypes are defined in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">[propertydatatypes]</code>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsection of the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uproperties.ini</code> file.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><em class=\"ph i\">Choice </em></td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Specifies a semicolon-separated list of acceptable values — only\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tfor use with data types that use the dropdown-box widget\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\ttype.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><em class=\"ph i\">Entries</em></td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Specifies the number of entries the Property Editor will accept.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTypically used for shorthand style definitions where multiple values\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tof the same type specify for example the top, bottom, left, and\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tright border. If not specifies, only 1 entry is allowed.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><em class=\"ph i\">AlternativeChoice</em></td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Specifies a semicolon-separated list of keywords that the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tProperty Editor will also accept as value, for example \"inherited\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"unset\", \"default\".</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"p\">For more details, see:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vfp1701664033439__ul_x4g_m4r_qzb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fxu1701663302440.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fxu1701663302440.html\" title=\"The web.ini file defines the physical UX web widget definitions where every section is a single widget definition. Each widget definition includes the name of the widget class that implements the client (browser) side of the widget, the JavaScript, Module, and CSS files that are required to run the widget class, some placeholder layout HTML used by the IDE and IDE property definitions, IncludeScript which refers to the widget specific ProcScript or JavaScript fragments to be included and the Interface Version using which the widget is implemented.\">web.ini</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"orx1701663500155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/orx1701663500155.html\" title=\"The uproperties.ini file defines the syntax of properties as well as property groups for web widgets.\">uproperties.ini</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"idk1665702794063.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/idk1665702794063.html\" title=\"Use the Component Editor to construct application components, such as dynamic and static server pages, and services.\">Component Editor</a></li>\n</ul></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vfp1701664033439__section_tbw_2pr_qzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d509580e282\">Example 1:</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vfp1701664033439_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vfp1701664033439__codeblock_oys_fpr_qzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[html:title]\ndescription=Title (Tooltip Text)\ncategory=Html\ntooltip=The title attribute specifies extra information about an element. The information is most often shown as a tooltip text when the mouse hovers over the element.\ndatatype=string</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vfp1701664033439__section_nq3_gpr_qzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d509580e294\">Example 2:</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vfp1701664033439_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vfp1701664033439__codeblock_oq3_gpr_qzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[html:type]\ndescription=Type\ncategory=Html\ntooltip=The type attribute specifies function of the input element.\ndatatype=choice\nchoice=button;checkbox;color;date;datetime;email;file;hidden;month;number;password;radio;range;search;tel;text;time;url;week</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vfp1701664033439__section_ywx_jpr_qzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d509580e305\">Example 3:</h2><div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vfp1701664033439_html_3\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vfp1701664033439__codeblock_s3j_mpr_qzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[style:flex-shrink]\ndescription=Flex Shrink\ncategory=Flex Item\ntooltip=Sets the shrink factor of a flex item.\ndatatype=positive_float\naltchoice=inherit;initial;revert;revert-layer;unset</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div><img alt=\"ux-PlainText widget properties\" class=\"image\" id=\"vfp1701664033439__image_pdb_wpr_qzb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/ux-plaintext-widget-properties.png?_LANG=enus\"/></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/orx1701663500155.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uproperties.ini</a><p>The uproperties.ini file defines the syntax of properties as well as property groups for web widgets.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5446196\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5446196\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[PropertyDefinition] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 This section, of which multiple are defined in the uproperties.ini file, defines a single property definition used by the Property Inspector of the DSP Component Editor in the IDE. Syntax Explain this code [PropertyId]= [html:title] description= Description category= Category tooltip= Tooltip datatype= DataType choice= Choice entries= Entries altchoice= AlternativeChoice Copy See the following table for syntax description: Syntax Description PropertyId Specifies the physical property id as it is maintained in the property list and supplied to your widget. The PropertyId is often prefixed with either html , style , or class separated by a colon. Other prefixes are also allowed but do not have a special treatment in Uniface. For example: html:title . The grp keyword is not allowed, as this is reserved for property groups. The following keywords are not allowed as PropertyId : propertydatatypes , propertygroups . The PropertyId is always send in lower case to the browser, regardless of how it is defined. It is good practice to not use camelcase for PropertyIds , but instead use hyphens (-) or underscores (_) as word separators. Description Specifies a more descriptive name or description of the property. It should be short, a single line, and is allowed to contain spaces. Category Specifies in which tab (category) the property will appear in the Property Inspector. Tooltip Specifies a more extensive description of the property. It might include a syntax or a reference to a standard W3C website describing the property. Sometimes it is useful to provide some examples. Use a semicolon to break your tooltip into multiple lines. Datatype Specifies the editing experience provided by the Property Inspector. Possible data types are defined in the [propertydatatypes] section of the uproperties.ini file. Choice Specifies a semicolon-separated list of acceptable values — only for use with data types that use the dropdown-box widget type. Entries Specifies the number of entries the Property Editor will accept. Typically used for shorthand style definitions where multiple values of the same type specify for example the top, bottom, left, and right border. If not specifies, only 1 entry is allowed. AlternativeChoice Specifies a semicolon-separated list of keywords that the Property Editor will also accept as value, for example \"inherited\", \"unset\", \"default\". For more details, see: web.ini uproperties.ini Component Editor Example 1: Explain this code [html:title] description=Title (Tooltip Text) category=Html tooltip=The title attribute specifies extra information about an element. The information is most often shown as a tooltip text when the mouse hovers over the element. datatype=string Copy Example 2: Explain this code [html:type] description=Type category=Html tooltip=The type attribute specifies function of the input element. datatype=choice choice=button;checkbox;color;date;datetime;email;file;hidden;month;number;password;radio;range;search;tel;text;time;url;week Copy Example 3: Explain this code [style:flex-shrink] description=Flex Shrink category=Flex Item tooltip=Sets the shrink factor of a flex item. datatype=positive_float altchoice=inherit;initial;revert;revert-layer;unset Copy Related Links uproperties.ini The uproperties.ini file defines the syntax of properties as well as property groups for web widgets. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}